rlStormCtrlEnbaleDependencyBetweenTypes.name: rlStormCtrlEnbaleDependencyBetweenTypes
rlStormCtrlEnbaleDependencyBetweenTypes.description: indicate enable limitation of dependency between frame types, such as enabling of multicast should be with the enabling of broadcast type (bcm 5632)

rlStormCtrlRateDependencyBetweenTypes.name: rlStormCtrlRateDependencyBetweenTypes
rlStormCtrlRateDependencyBetweenTypes.description: indicate limitation of dependency between frame types for rate assignment, for example: assigning of rate limit for unicast frame must assigning the same rate for multicast and bradcast frame (bcm 5615), in case the device support enbale per each frame type but with the same rate limitation.

rlStormCtrlUnknownUnicastRate.name: rlStormCtrlUnknownUnicastRate
rlStormCtrlUnknownUnicastRate.description: set the storm control rate limit for the unknown unicast frames, 0 indicate blocking of frames from this type.

rlStormCtrlBroadcastRate.name: rlStormCtrlBroadcastRate
